<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-17834] Repair coordinator can get stuck in an infinite loop if it gets a FailSession after it&apos;s marked a session FINALIZED</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-17834</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If the repair coordinator gets a FailSession message after it has marked the session as FINALIZED it will start an infinite loop of FailSession messages. This is unique to 4.0+ in &lt;tt&gt;CoordinatorSession.java&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
